  "body": "<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://file.garden/ZWUae22eyH6XVW5v/digestive_title.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"509\" height=\"95\" /></p>\n<p>A simple mod that adds objects that you can eat that are not edible in real life(Don't do it IRL pls!)</p>\n<p>Currently adds:</p>\n<p>- Crayons</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://file.garden/ZWUae22eyH6XVW5v/crayons.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"369\" height=\"208\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Recipes:<br /><img src=\"https://file.garden/ZWUae22eyH6XVW5v/crafting.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"347\" height=\"195\" /></p>\n<p>Replace dye with other colors for other crayons</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Future plans:</p>\n<p>Spoons</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Modog500000/digestive\"><img src=\"https://file.garden/ZWUae22eyH6XVW5v/github.png\" width=\"277\" height=\"277\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUPyn9ITA0e_vkCjc1Olttw\"><img src=\"https://file.garden/ZWUae22eyH6XVW5v/youtube.png\" width=\"277\" height=\"277\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.volcanobay.xyz\"><img src=\"https://file.garden/ZWUae22eyH6XVW5v/discord.png\" width=\"277\" height=\"277\" /></a></p>",
